  "text": "The proof of this proposition is given in Section 2. Now we make a special choice of \u03c6(\u03b6) and \u03d5(\u03b6) in Proposition 1.2 and define the particular solutions n (0) , . . . , n (5) of (1.32). Recall the rays \u03a3 0 , . . . , \u03a3 5 defined in (1.10) (see also Figure 1 ). We define the trivalent contours \u0393 (0) , . . . , \u0393 [CITATION_1] as the \u0393 in Proposition 1.2 as follows:",
